HEADWORD: Novosibirsk
<hw>Novosibirsk</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A city in the Asian part
of Russia. Much Soviet military research was performed there, and until
the 1990's it was restricted from entry by foreigners.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

